":3,"quote":{"pid":"8a1cd77d42b8727a0cca532fe761fc73a67f433b","tid":2436643,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T09:49:53.000Z","msg":"《環球時報》記者提問：「近期美國和一些西方國家誣衊中國在新疆地區採取行動構成「種族滅絕」，對於這種誣衊您怎麼看待？中方怎麼回應？」<br />\n<br />\n王毅說：<br />\n<br />\n「說到「種族滅絕」，大多數人想到的是16世紀的北美印第安人，19世紀的非洲黑奴，20世紀的猶太人，以及至今仍在堅持抗爭的澳洲原住民。」<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://china.hket. com/article/2894654</code></pre>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T10:04:21.000Z","msg":"成吉思汗打到歐洲 奸咗幾多女人？"},{"pid":"c502d38a69a4eebe6c155c2bff0b3c0de95bc956","tid":2436643,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T10:04:38.000Z","msg":"即係有發生？"},{"pid":"e833b625b23abf99d4fcdc56e1982c570816862a","tid":2436643,"uid":53855,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"736c1100e3e0cd4ad2ec23125c5e5eed06dd991b","tid":2436643,"uid":28547,"like":110,"dislike":0,"score":110,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T09:51:01.000Z","msg":"唔係南京大屠殺？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T10:05:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E6%B9%98%E5%86%9B%E5%8D%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%B1%A0%E5%9F%8E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E6%25B9%2598%25E5%2586%259B%25E5%258D%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E5%25B1%25A0%25E5%259F%258E&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bOr6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=d361d3eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E6%B9%98%E5%86%9B%E5%8D%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%B1%A0%E5%9F%8E</a><br />\n<br />\n湘軍南京屠城，是發生在1864年7月，曾國藩弟曾國荃率湘軍攻破當時的太平天國首都天京（今南京市）後開始縱火殺掠，屠殺平民的事件，總計死者約二、三十萬人（死亡人數有爭議）。。太平天國強盛時，南京有100多萬人，到了光緒帝登基時，南京依然人口不足50萬。南京百姓至今仍以「曾老饕」、「曾剃頭」、「曾屠戶」等詞稱呼曾國藩、曾國荃兄弟。"},{"pid":"524baf4c6e0e35abea63740804733ceebfb4e060","tid":2436643,"uid":156913,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c502d38a69a4eebe6c155c2bff0b3c0de95bc956","tid":2436643,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T10:04:38.000Z","msg":"即係有發生？"},"citedBy":0,"